## **ðŸ›  Tech Stack**  
| Component       | Technology |  
|----------------|------------|  
| **Frontend**   | React, Chart.js, TailwindCSS |  
| **Backend**    | Node.js, Express |  
| **Database**   | MongoDB (Atlas) |  
| **Auth**       | JWT, OAuth 2.0 |  
| **AI/NLP**     | TensorFlow.js, Universal Sentence Encoder |  

---

## **ðŸ”Œ API Integration**  
### **Available Endpoints**  
| Endpoint | Method | Description |  
|----------|--------|-------------|  
| `/api/auth/signup` | POST | User registration |  
| `/api/auth/login` | POST | User login |  
| `/api/chat` | POST | Get AI chatbot response |  
| `/api/journal` | GET/POST | Fetch or add journal entries |  
| `/api/analytics` | GET | Mood trend data |  

### **Example Request (Chatbot)**  
```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/api/chat \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"message": "I feel anxious today"}'
```

